## Solution.

$a+2016, b+2016, a+b$ is an arithmetic sequence, so

$$
\begin{aligned}
b+2016 & =\frac{a+2016+a+b}{2} \\
a & =\frac{b+2016}{2}
\end{aligned}
$$

$a, 2016, b$ is a geometric sequence with $q=\frac{2016}{a}=\frac{b}{2016}$.

It follows that $a b=2016^{2}$.

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \frac{b+2016}{2} \cdot b=2016^{2} \\
& b^{2}+2016 b-2 \cdot 2016^{2}=0
\end{aligned}
$$

It follows that

